Package: lcde.toolbox
Type: Package
Title: LCDE Toolbox: Tools for Analyzing and Visualizing Educational Data
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(person("Pedro", "Sartori Dias dos Reis", email = "pedrosartdr@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0005-5819-7103")), person("Rafael", "Naime Ruggiero", email = "rafaruggiero@usp.br", role = c("ctb")), person("Mozart", "Neves Ramos", email = "mozartnramos@gmail.com", role = c("ctb")))
Maintainer: Laboratório de Ciência de Dados em Educação (LCDE) - Sérgio Henrique Ferreira Chair, Institute of Advanced Studies - Ribeirão Preto, University of São Paulo (IEA-RP/USP) <catedraiearp@usp.br>
Description: Provides tools for analyzing and visualizing educational data, including the creation of charts, georeferenced maps, principal component analyses (PCA), and automatic generation of presentations. Features a comprehensive set of functions for conducting detailed analyses, generating standardized reports, and creating interactive visualizations to support evidence-based decision-making in the education sector.
